```text
恢复报告：
- 菜单恢复：PASS/FAIL
- 回调可达：PASS/FAIL
- Skill分组：PASS/FAIL
- 监控策略：PASS/FAIL
- 缺失项=N
RESULT: PASS/FAIL
```


